OL,3,CFears 28-day gap between bin
OL,4,Ccollections will attract rats
OL,6,FResidents in part of Cheltenham have
OL,7,Fsaid they're unhappy they won't have
OL,8,Fsome bins collected for nearly a month
OL,9,Fover Christmas.
OL,11,FIt comes as councils across the South
OL,12,FWest consider cutting collections for
OL,13,Fhousehold waste - in a bid to save
OL,14,Fmoney and improve recycling rates.
OL,16,FCurrently most general waste bins are
OL,17,Fcollected every fortnight, but several
OL,18,Flocal authorities are now extending
OL,19,Fthe time between pick ups.
