OL,3,CFears 28-day gap between bin
OL,4,Ccollections will attract rats
OL,6,F"It could be a problem for people with
OL,7,Ffamilies," Clive Wilce, told ITV News
OL,8,Fas he faces a 28-day wait for his next
OL,9,Fgeneral waste collection.
OL,11,F"We've got a problem with rats in the
OL,12,Fback lane," he added. "If there's food
OL,13,Fwaste left, there's going to be vermin
OL,14,Fabout isn't there."
OL,16,FThe council said the temporary
OL,17,Finconvenience is designed to give
OL,18,Fworkers a much-needed voice and it
OL,19,Fisn't becoming common practice.
