OL,3,CFears 28-day gap between bin
OL,4,Ccollections will attract rats
OL,6,FCllr Izzaac Tailford, from Cheltenham
OL,7,FBorough Council, said: "We'd like to
OL,8,Fdo this for Christmas for those waste
OL,9,Fand recycling teams.
OL,11,F"But for general week-to-week, I have
OL,12,Fno intention to change how frequently
OL,13,Fwe collect the bins."
OL,15,FSomerset Council has already moved to
OL,16,Fthree-weekly household waste
OL,17,Fcollections. In Bristol, leaked
OL,18,Fdocuments suggest four-weekly bin
OL,19,Fcollections are being considered by
OL,20,Fthe Green administration.
