OL,3,CFears 28-day gap between bin
OL,4,Ccollections will attract rats
OL,6,FAlthough no decision has been made it
OL,7,Fhas sparked a lot of debate.
OL,9,F"People who fill their bins up before
OL,10,Fthe two weeks are over stick it in our
OL,11,Fbin," one resident told ITV News. "So
OL,12,FI don't think it's a good idea (to
OL,13,Freduce collections) to be honest."
OL,15,FOne other resident said: "Usually
OL,16,Fafter two weeks we have plenty of
OL,17,Frubbish as it is, the bin is usually
OL,18,Ffull. So after four weeks we'd be
OL,19,Foverpowered with rubbish."
