OL,3,CFears 28-day gap between bin
OL,4,Ccollections will attract rats
OL,6,FHead of the Labour Group Tom Renhard
OL,7,Fhas started a petition opposing plans
OL,8,Fto cut bin collections in Bristol
OL,9,Fwhich has since been signed by almost
OL,10,F2,000 people.
OL,12,F"We think it's total madness," he said.
OL,14,F"We've got issues with fly-tipping
OL,15,Facross the city, we've got issues with
OL,16,Fbin collections and recycling
OL,17,Fcollections at the moment not
OL,18,Fhappening at the frequency they
OL,19,Fshould. That service needs sorting out
OL,20,Fbefore we start looking at anything
OL,21,Felse in terms of reducing frequency."
