OL,6,FA Bristol City Council spokesperson
OL,7,Ftold ITV News all options are
OL,8,Fcurrently draft proposals and no
OL,9,Fdecisions on recycling and black bin
OL,10,Fcollections will be made until the
OL,11,Fentire city is consulted.
OL,13,FBut there are many authorities moving
OL,14,Ftowards three-weekly collections,
OL,15,Fincluding South Gloucestershire
OL,16,FCouncil and North Somerset Council.
